@startuml
!includeurl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/proveo-ca/identity/refs/heads/main/proveo.iuml
actor User
participant "SolidJS UI" as SolidJS
participant "Stockfish Web Worker\n(stockfish-18-lite.js)" as StockfishWorker
participant "Ktor Server" as Ktor
participant "Harness Daemon" as Harness
participant "State Analyzer" as Analyzer
participant "Strategy Agent" as Strategy
participant "Dialogue Agent" as Dialogue
participant "Kotlin Tools (Validator/Bridge)" as Tools
participant "Stockfish" as Stockfish

== Hint Request Flow (Local Worker) ==
User -> SolidJS: Clicks "Get Hint"
SolidJS -> StockfishWorker: uci / isready (once)
SolidJS -> StockfishWorker: position fen <current>
SolidJS -> StockfishWorker: go depth 10
StockfishWorker --> SolidJS: bestmove e2e4
SolidJS -> User: Displays hint (bestmove)

== Hover Blunder Flow (Local Worker) ==
User -> SolidJS: Hovers candidate move square
SolidJS -> StockfishWorker: position fen <after hypothetical move>
SolidJS -> StockfishWorker: go depth 6
StockfishWorker --> SolidJS: info score cp -250 ...
SolidJS -> User: Hover override advice + shocked emotion

== Replayability Flow (Local History) ==
User -> SolidJS: Clicks "Back" / "Forward"
SolidJS -> SolidJS: Update currentIndex in gameState
SolidJS -> User: Renders historical FEN (no API call)

== Standard Move Flow (Move + Advice) ==
User -> SolidJS: Click-to-move (e2 -> e4)
SolidJS -> Ktor: POST /move { humanMoveSan: "e4",\nfenAfterHuman: "<fen>", difficulty: "<difficulty>" }
Ktor -> Harness: JSON-line: { command: "move", ... }

note over Harness, Stockfish: AI move generation (engine-assisted)

Harness -> Tools: Validate and compute response move
Tools -> Stockfish: UCI search (best move)
Stockfish --> Tools: bestmove e7e5
Tools --> Harness: AI move resolved

Harness --> Ktor: JSON-line: { fen: "<updated>", move: "e7e5" }
Ktor --> SolidJS: HTTP 200 OK { fen: "<updated>", move: "e7e5" }
SolidJS -> User: Renders updated position

SolidJS -> Ktor: POST /advice { humanMove: "e4", aiMove: "e7e5", fen: "<updated>" }

note over Harness, Dialogue: Coaching commentary generation

Ktor -> Harness: JSON-line: { command: "advice", ... }
Harness -> Analyzer: Analyze position (evaluation context)
Analyzer -> Tools: Get Evaluation (FEN)
Tools -> Stockfish: eval
Stockfish --> Tools: score cp 45
Tools --> Analyzer: Evaluation (+0.45)

Harness -> Dialogue: Generate coaching advice
Dialogue --> Harness: Advice text
Harness --> Ktor: JSON-line: { advice: "..." }
Ktor --> SolidJS: HTTP 200 OK { advice: "..." }
SolidJS -> User: Displays coach advice (and emotion)

@enduml
